Company Overview of Seligman Global Fund Series, Inc. - Seligman Global Growth Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of August 17, 2009 Seligman Global Fund Series, Inc. - Seligman Global Growth Fund has been acquired by Threadneedle Global Equity Fund. Seligman Global Fund Series, Inc. - Seligman Global Growth Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Columbia Management Investment Advisers, LLC. The fund is co managed by Wellington Management Company, LLP. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The fund invests in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in growth stocks of large and mid cap companies. The fund employs fundamental analysis along with a bottom up stock picking approach focusing on factors like focusing ...
As of August 17, 2009 Seligman Global Fund Series, Inc. - Seligman Global Growth Fund has been acquired by Threadneedle Global Equity Fund. Seligman Global Fund Series, Inc. - Seligman Global Growth Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Columbia Management Investment Advisers, LLC. The fund is co managed by Wellington Management Company, LLP. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The fund invests in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in growth stocks of large and mid cap companies. The fund employs fundamental analysis along with a bottom up stock picking approach focusing on factors like focusing on companies with accelerating fundamentals or earnings growth with consideration paid to valuations, quality management, strong possibility of multiple expansion, and unique competitive advantages to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI World Index and MSCI World Growth Index. The fund was formerly known as Seligman Henderson Global Growth Opportunities Fund. Seligman Global Fund Series, Inc. - Seligman Global Growth Fund was formed on May 27, 1999 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


225 Franklin StreetBoston, MA 02110United StatesFounded in 1999



Phone: 617-385-9580

Fax: 877-303-7454








